data.description: Come check out this home in Norfolk, near shopping & military bases! VA assumable loan available – because who doesn't love a good deal? Open layout for hosting dinners or homebodies, cozy bedrooms for nap enthusiasts, and a kitchen that'll make Gordon Ramsay jealous. Deck for sunbathing or stargazing, all surrounded by a fence to keep all your fur babies in their back yard oasis. Solar panels to save on electricity and your wallet. Schedule a tour before it's gone!
